<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Khawvel pathien tam mahlele,
 I pau khat mai van ah a um hi;
 Pien tung neilo, Bul-leh-tawp chuh ahi!

[V2]
 Aw, U-le-nau leh nu-leh-patehaw,
 I Pathien tak hun bel tau uo;
 Lung kisik in, ngaihtuoh thawn puo'n lau.

[V3]
 2. Zuouthei pathien hinna neilo,
 'Ka nei,' ti'n mi a puimang zo hi;
 A neihsun chu Gehen ahi ngal a.

[V4]
 3. Beimang pathien nunsiepa chun,
 A sep leh a kipahna pen chuh;
 Thagau Gehen a puihlut hi ahi.

[V5]
 4. Ngaiun, Lungsietna Pathien chun,
 A Cha mangte hawldawkna ding in;
 A Cha khat lengleng chuh A hun sawlta'i.</lyrics>
<title>THERE IS ONLY ONE GOD</title>
<author>Zawmpau</author>
<hymn_number>29</hymn_number>
</song>